text: Quinty Schoens (born 12 February 1999) is a Dutch triathlete and professional racing cyclist, who currently rides since 2022 for UCI Women's Continental Team Parkhotel Valkenburg Cycling Team. Van Rooijen earned a contract with Parkhotel Valkenburg Cycling Team in 2022. She competed during her first year of a professional cyclist at the 2022 Tour de France Femmes. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch cyclists Category:Sportspeople from Limburg (Netherlands) Category:Sportswomen Category:Triathletes
